trans-unit.source: Provides special handling information to inform event listeners whether specific handlers should be invoked.
trans-unit.target: 提供特殊的处理信息以通知事件侦听器是否应该调用特定的处理程序。

trans-unit.source: Determines whether objects are equivalent.
trans-unit.target: 确定对象是否等效。

trans-unit.source: The object to compare to the current <see cref="T:System.Windows.RoutedEventHandlerInfo" />.
trans-unit.target: 要与当前 <see cref="T:System.Windows.RoutedEventHandlerInfo" /> 比较的对象。

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the specified object is equivalent to the current <see cref="T:System.Windows.RoutedEventHandlerInfo" />.
trans-unit.target: 确定指定的对象是否等效于当前的 <see cref="T:System.Windows.RoutedEventHandlerInfo" />。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the specified object is equivalent to the current <see cref="T:System.Windows.RoutedEventHandlerInfo" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果指定的对象等效于当前的 <see cref="T:System.Windows.RoutedEventHandlerInfo" />，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Windows.RoutedEventHandlerInfo" /> to compare to the current <see cref="T:System.Windows.RoutedEventHandlerInfo" />.
trans-unit.target: 要与当前 <see cref="T:System.Windows.RoutedEventHandlerInfo" /> 进行比较的 <see cref="T:System.Windows.RoutedEventHandlerInfo" />。

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the specified <see cref="T:System.Windows.RoutedEventHandlerInfo" /> is equivalent to the current <see cref="T:System.Windows.RoutedEventHandlerInfo" />.
trans-unit.target: 确定指定的 <see cref="T:System.Windows.RoutedEventHandlerInfo" /> 是否与当前的 <see cref="T:System.Windows.RoutedEventHandlerInfo" /> 等效。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the specified <see cref="T:System.Windows.RoutedEventHandlerInfo" /> is equivalent to the current <see cref="T:System.Windows.RoutedEventHandlerInfo" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果指定的 <see cref="T:System.Windows.RoutedEventHandlerInfo" /> 与当前的 <see cref="T:System.Windows.RoutedEventHandlerInfo" /> 等效，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: This implementation relies on value equivalence of the <xref:System.Windows.RoutedEventHandlerInfo.Handler%2A><xref:System.Windows.RoutedEventHandlerInfo.InvokeHandledEventsToo%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: 此实现依赖于值等效性<xref:System.Windows.RoutedEventHandlerInfo.Handler%2A><xref:System.Windows.RoutedEventHandlerInfo.InvokeHandledEventsToo%2A>属性。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.RoutedEventHandlerInfo.Handler%2A> property is a delegate reference.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.RoutedEventHandlerInfo.Handler%2A>属性是委托引用。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, equivalence implies a duplicate reference to the same handler.
trans-unit.target: 因此，等效性意味着对相同的处理程序的重复引用。

trans-unit.source: Returns a hash code for the current <see cref="T:System.Windows.RoutedEventHandlerInfo" />.
trans-unit.target: 返回当前 <see cref="T:System.Windows.RoutedEventHandlerInfo" /> 的哈希代码。

trans-unit.source: A hash code for the current <see cref="T:System.Windows.RoutedEventHandlerInfo" />.
trans-unit.target: 当前 <see cref="T:System.Windows.RoutedEventHandlerInfo" /> 的哈希代码。

trans-unit.source: Gets the event handler.
trans-unit.target: 获取事件处理程序。

trans-unit.source: The event handler.
trans-unit.target: 事件处理程序。

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the event handler is invoked when the routed event is marked handled.
trans-unit.target: 获取一个值，该值指示将路由事件标记为已处理后是否调用事件处理程序。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the event handler is invoked when the routed event is marked handled; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果将路由事件标记为已处理后调用事件处理程序，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: The first object to compare.
trans-unit.target: 要比较的第一个对象。

trans-unit.source: The second object to compare.
trans-unit.target: 要比较的第二个对象。

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the specified objects are equivalent.
trans-unit.target: 确定指定的对象是否等效。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the objects are equivalent; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果对象等效，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.target: 要比较的第一个对象。

trans-unit.source: The second object to compare.
trans-unit.target: 要比较的第二个对象。

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the specified objects are not equivalent.
trans-unit.target: 确定指定的对象是否不等效。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the objects are not equivalent; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果对象不等效，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。
